{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into a first-person indie horror as you take on the role of John, a real estate agent invited to assess a mysterious old mansion. However, what starts as a simple assessment quickly turns into a desperate fight for survival when John finds himself trapped in a sinister nightmare within the ancient walls of the mansion. Explore the dark secrets, face unknown threats, and uncover the truth behind the mansion's mystery as you struggle for your own life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Nightmare in the Old Mansion&quot; is a first-person indie horror game of the walking simulator genre where the average time to complete the game is 50 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2982920/extras/gif3.gif?t=1738520652\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Main Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tense and dynamic atmosphere</strong>: Perfect for those seeking an intense and unpredictable horror experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Realistic and immersive graphics</strong>: Gameplay that makes you feel like you're truly in the mansion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Intriguing narrative</strong>: Explore every corner of the mansion while uncovering its mysteries.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Impactful choices</strong>: Each decision can shape the character's fate.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Alternate endings</strong>: Your actions can lead to different outcomes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ADULT CONTENT DESCRIPTION</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Nightmare in the Old Mansion&quot; contains scenes of violence that may have a negative impact and is not suitable for all ages.</p>","background":"https:/